      "comboUsage": "",
      "strategicPurpose": "",
      "iconName": "Abysm_Strike",
      "tips": "\"Dyrroth quickly charges and releases Fatal Strike, dealing Physical Damage to enemies along the way and slowing them down. This is the core skill for Dyrroth to deal damage. The skill takes a certain amount of time to cast, but the damage is nothing to take lightly. So you need to find the right time to release the full potential of this skill. \"\"Spectre Step\"\" with its own enhancement has a better use effect.\"",
